{
  "text": "Antigen slides, conjugate and control sera were obtained from the OVI. Batches of antigen slides were removed from storage at -20 \u00b0C, incubated at 37 \u00b0C for 10 min and then fixed in cold acetone at -20 \u00b0C. Two-fold dilutions, of the test and control sera, starting at 1/40, 1/80 and 1/160, were prepared using PBS [CITATION_1] . A drop (~ 4 \u03bc\u2113) of each diluted serum was pipetted into each respective circle of the antigen slide, incubated at 37 \u00b0C for 30 min and then washed off with PBS.",
